            <Title>conclusion</Title>
            <Text>In conclusion, in the literature of sensibility as a whole, the healing and cosmopolitan potential of benevolence soon falls apart, but it’s a good idea, and the attention to the body is also a good idea. The literature of sensibility tries to nourish suffering, which is a vulnerable position but a valuable goal.</Text>
